Retirement and Investing
Get more from your money. 
Making good financial decisions now can put you in a better position tomorrow - and a Financial Consultant from Citizens Investment Services is here to help you.










Questions? Ask a Citizen.


Questions? Ask a Citizen.




1-800-242-2224













Retirement Planning


Living in Retirement


Education Planning


General Investing






Retirement Planning
Retirement plans help to fund your future while keeping your present needs in mind. Ready to plan ahead? Ask a Financial consultant to help you create a plan.
EXPLORE RETIREMENT STRATEGIES 




Living in Retirement
Retirement brings its own set of goals and challenges - and your assets need to keep pace with your aspirations. Our Financial Consultants can help you with retirement income strategies.
GET A PLAN IN PLACE 




Education Planning
With the cost of college tuition, it's never too early to start investing in your child's education. A Financial Consultant can help you with custodial accounts and 529 College Savings Plans.
START A COLLEGE SAVINGS PLAN 




General Investing
Whether you're a seasoned investor or a curious beginner, our Financial Consultants can help you build a diversified portfolio that may contain stocks, bonds, mutual funds, and other investments.
LEARN MORE ABOUT INVESTING 


















